lead_paragraph: Championship leader Nico Rosberg set himself at odds with Formula One stewards and his Mercedes team mate Lewis Hamilton after another costly collision at the Austrian Grand Prix on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Rosberg on Another Collision Course With Hamilton
